# Implementation Plan: AgriPredict Architecture & AI Features

This plan integrates the user's comprehensive architectural vision (stunning UI, ML integration principles, feature pages) using **pure HTML, CSS, and Vanilla JavaScript** as requested, avoiding any frontend frameworks (no React, Next.js, or Tailwind). The backend will remain Express + SQLite for rapid MVP delivery.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Tech Stack:** I have completely removed React, Vite, Tailwind, Framer Motion, and Recharts. The frontend will be built from scratch using 100% native HTML, custom CSS for the requested design system (glassmorphism, animations), and vanilla JavaScript.
> - **AI & ML Pipeline:** For the MVP, we will use LLMs via API keys (OpenAI) to simulate the XGBoost/Random Forest predictions, giving you immediate, realistic AI outputs for Crop Yield, Confidence Scores, and Recommendations without needing to train a model from scratch right now.

